Our Gentoo Overlay with useful ebuilds.


To use simply do:
  git clone git://github.com/doubledrones/gentoo_overlay.git /usr/local/portage

And insert these lines to /etc/make.conf
  # If you have layman installed, this line must be below the layman make.conf line
  PORTDIR_OVERLAY="${PORTDIR_OVERLAY} /usr/local/portage/"
